{"tid":1160572,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"若小昭不悔敏我潮文！！！！","createTime":"2019-05-18T14:36:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T19:15:05.000Z","uid":225828,"like":7,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"f88f7745426b45cf3381b5356c26669a312b3fe1","tid":1160572,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T14:36:52.000Z","msg":"同時愛四個咁花心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望<span style=\"color: blue;\">芷若</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">敏敏</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">不悔</span>、<span style=\"color: teal;\">小昭</span>一齊懲罰我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n芷若罸我要同佢嘴對嘴<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JOvDHQX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJOvDHQX.jpg&h=9fac6947&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n，嘴到佢滿意，如果唔係就鞭我pat pat<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dwTJThX.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdwTJThX.gif&h=b487829b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n敏敏一邊「小淫賊～小淫賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」咁鬧我<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xnOFeEZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxnOFeEZ.gif&h=0a68d352&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n，一邊用佢隻腳丫子懲罰到我隻巨龍嘔白泡<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/36mC1c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F36mC1c2.jpg&h=f9f5f52a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不悔要我啜乾淨飲乾淨唒佢F cup啲母乳<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jO4Ui8A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjO4Ui8A.png&h=afde5ef4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n，如果唔係就用對奶焗暈我再吸走我啲陽氣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ehyvbn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ehyvbn.jpg&h=9729e0a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小昭最離譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，用啲鎖鏈將我同佢綁埋一齊，罸我時時刻刻都要攬實佢，佢唔凖就唔畀放手，出到街畀人恥笑羞辱到無地自容都要攬實佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nNzMO0o.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnNzMO0o.gif&h=a7ab61b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n，佢仲話想用啲鏈嚟鎖住我嘅靈魂，痴線架<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M36LqjV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM36LqjV.gif&h=145534ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">嗚呀！睇嚟我生生世世都要做佢哋嘅愛的俘虜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iTf0PaJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiTf0PaJ.gif&h=72805760&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f9f843970e836de7afcbd9d9ab2fcf9bb9ec332a","tid":1160572,"uid":94828,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T14:41:39.000Z","msg":"0.5/10以作鼓勵"},{"pid":"0085f4ce2059ae2aa9991eef534fa0b8f215be7f","tid":1160572,"uid":196536,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T08:49:13.000Z","msg":"食藥啊"},{"pid":"2